Revision history for MojoX-Session

{{$NEXT}}

0.32
        - Add a persistent attribute to MojoX::Session to set if Cookie is
		  persistent or not. (default = 1) which gives backward
		  compatibility with previous version. You can upgrade your db with
		  this query:
		    ALTER TABLE YOUR_SESSION_TABLE_NAME ADD COLUMN
			  `persistent` tinyint(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '1';
        - Changes in other files to support this new attribute
        - Solved a bug in Mojolicious::Plugin::Session
		- Removed a warning in dbic test

0.31 2014-01-07T08:04:08Z

        - Just meta files update

0.30 2013-10-18T08:16:12Z

        - Support httponly flag (Sergey Homenkow)

0.29 2013-10-10T16:51:24Z

        - Fix test compatibility with v4.45

